Package: ggdag
Title: A Package for Working with Directed Acyclic Graphs
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Malcolm", "Barrett", email = "malcolmbarrett@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: `ggdag` is a package to simplify working with directed acyclic graphs (DAGs) in R. `ggdag` is built on top of `dagitty`, an R package that uses the dagitty web tool for creating and analyzing DAGs. `ggdag` provides functionality for tidying and plotting `dagitty` objects using `ggplot2` and `ggraph`, as well as common analytic and graphical functions, such as determining adjustment sets and node relartionships. 
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.0.0),
    ggplot2,
    ggraph
